---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-white dark:bg-black border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-void-800 pt-16 pb-8 text-center md:text-left relative z-10 transition-colors duration-500">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-12">   
        <div class="md:col-span-2">
            <a href="/" class="inline-block hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity shrink-0">  
                <img 
                    src="/logo-light.png" 
                    alt="S.E. Deracy" 
                    class="w-auto object-contain block dark:hidden h-[clamp(60px,10vw,90px)]" 
                />
                <img 
                    src="/logo-dark.png" 
                    alt="S.E. Deracy" 
                    class="w-auto object-contain hidden dark:block h-[clamp(60px,10vw,90px)]" 
                />
            </a>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-sm mx-auto md:mx-0 leading-relaxed">
                Weaving worlds with code and chaos. Architect of the <em>Elementless</em> universe.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <h4 class="text-lilac-dark dark:text-gold font-serif font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-l mb-6">Explore</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-4 font-sans text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                <li><a href="/books" class="hover:text-lilac-dark dark:hover:text-gold transition">Books</a></li>
                <li><a href="/map" class="hover:text-lilac-dark dark:hover:text-gold transition">Map of Eurion</a></li>
                <li><a href="/about" class="hover:text-lilac-dark dark:hover:text-gold transition">About the Author</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
            <h4 class="text-lilac-dark dark:text-gold font-serif font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-l mb-6">Connect</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-4 font-sans text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                <li>
                    <a href="mailto:contact@sederacy.com" class="hover:text-lilac-dark dark:hover:text-gold transition flex items-center gap-2 justify-center md:justify-start">
                        Contact via Email
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/#newsletter" class="hover:text-lilac-dark dark:hover:text-gold transition flex items-center gap-2 justify-center md:justify-start">
                        Join the Council
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://github.com/sderacy" target="_blank" class="hover:text-lilac-dark dark:hover:text-gold transition flex items-center gap-2 justify-center md:justify-start">
                        GitHub
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-void-800 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">
        <p>&copy; {currentYear} S.E. Deracy. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 md:mt-0">Site made with <span class="text-lilac-dark dark:text-gold"> ‚ù§ </span> by S.E. Deracy.</p>
    </div>
</footer>